Author: LovarAi
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Lovar - Artificial Intelligence:The Future of Investing
Body: Yes, token-holders will be investing in a profitable trading algorithm. We will be working to improve the algorithm and adding new features over time. In recent testing, LovarAI was able to achieve average daily profit margins upwards of 3.57%.

Author: LovarAi
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Lovar - Artificial Intelligence:The Future of Investing
Body: Our tests and trading experience have shown profits above the range of returns specified for long term and short term deposits. Profits earned above our specified rates will be reserved for Lovar. Investors will be able to view detailed AI analytics from the ‘AI Analytics’ tab of our dashboard. All Lovar fees are none to minimal. For detailed information, please refer to our white paper.
